{"tid":639266,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳茂波就坐紅色車現身殉職警喪禮致歉","createTime":"2018-04-23T10:49:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T10:49:06.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7cdded8695fa5a1a4798e12ff5172a7444856f87","tid":639266,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T10:49:06.000Z","msg":"西九龍交通部高級警員林海雲（51歲），上月在東九龍走廊處理一宗交通意外期間，遭一輛駛至的密斗貨車撞斃。警方今日為林海雲舉行最高榮譽喪禮，多名高官均有到場致意，不過財政司司長陳茂波上午乘座其FS紅色座駕到場，被指對喪禮不敬。財政司辦公室回覆《蘋果》時表示，陳對林海雲先生及其家人並無不敬之意，就此表示摯誠歉意。<br />\n<br />\n財政司辦公室表示，財政司長現時使用的座駕由前任司長在2016年年底選用，上任後並無更換座駕或更改顏色。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180423/58108181\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180423%2F58108181&d=8RN%2B%2FEQFj5W3xOX7Koq%2F44M9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=5c02ff38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180423%2F58108181&h=62fa625e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180423/58108181</a>"}]}